OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said a
OL,7,Fnew agreement with Saudi Arabia on a
OL,8,Fcivilian nuclear programme will
OL,9,Frequire the kingdom to normalise
OL,10,Frelations with Israel through the
OL,11,FAbraham Accords.
OL,13,FThe Abraham Accords are a series of
OL,14,Flandmark normalisation agreements
OL,15,Fbetween Israel and several Arab
OL,16,Fnations, brokered by the US, to which
OL,17,FSaudi Arabia is not currently a
OL,18,Fsignatory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
