PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FIn a post on social media on Thursday,
OL,7,FTrump said the deal does not allow
OL,8,FSaudi Arabia to enrich uranium.
OL,10,FHowever, non-proliferation experts
OL,11,Fhave raised concerns that the
OL,12,Fagreement does not include sufficient
OL,13,Fsafeguards to prevent uranium
OL,14,Fenrichment reaching weapons-grade
OL,15,Flevels.
OL,17,FTrump's post said the agreement "will
OL,18,Fbe approved, but is totally subject to
OL,19,FSaudi Arabia joining the very
OL,20,Frespected and successful Abraham
OL,21,FAccords".
OL,26,@yD@aOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
