OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FHe added that the US "is not opposed
OL,7,Fto Civil (Non-Enriched) Nuclear
OL,8,FFacilities".
OL,10,FSaudi Arabia has made it clear that
OL,11,Fnormalising relations with Israel
OL,12,Fwould first require the establishment
OL,13,Fof a clear pathway towards Palestinian
OL,14,Fstatehood.
OL,16,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,17,FNetanyahu has rejected the idea of
OL,18,FPalestinian statehood, saying it would
OL,19,Fbe a threat to Israel's security.
OL,26,@nD@VOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FThe Saudi embassy in Washington
OL,7,Fdeclined to comment on Thursday on
OL,8,FTrump's assertion that the nuclear
OL,9,Fdeal would require the kingdom to join
OL,10,Fthe Accords.
OL,12,FNetanyahu's office welcomed the
OL,13,Fprospect of Saudi Arabia joining the
OL,14,FAccords in a statement, describing it
OL,15,Fas a "historic leap forward for peace
OL,16,Fin the Middle East".
OL,18,FHowever, the statement made no mention
OL,19,Fof the agreement to expand Saudi
OL,20,FArabia's civilian nuclear programme.
OL,26,@wD@FOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
