FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FTrump has sought to build on the 2020
OL,7,Fagreements, which expanded the number
OL,8,Fof Arab and Muslim-majority countries
OL,9,Fwith diplomatic ties with Israel.
OL,11,FSaudi Arabia is the most influential
OL,12,FArab power in the Middle East, and
OL,13,FTrump believes the kingdom joining the
OL,14,Faccords is key to achieving long-term
OL,15,Fstability in the region.
OL,17,FThe new nuclear agreement announced on
OL,18,FWednesday is expected to last 30 years
OL,19,Fand involve US companies in developing
OL,20,FSaudi Arabia's civilian nuclear
OL,21,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
