PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FIt could allow the construction of a
OL,7,Furanium enrichment facility in the
OL,8,Fkingdom following a joint US-Saudi
OL,9,Fstudy.
OL,11,FThe agreement will be submitted to
OL,12,FCongress for review, according to the
OL,13,FUS and Saudi governments.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
