FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FThe deal does not include the
OL,7,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency's
OL,8,F"additional protocol", which would
OL,9,Fallow for greater monitoring,
OL,10,Finspections and verification,
OL,11,Faccording to a person familiar with
OL,12,Fthe decision.
OL,14,FSaudi Arabia's Energy Ministry said
OL,15,Fthe agreement would support efforts to
OL,16,F"diversify energy sources, advance
OL,17,Fcutting-edge technologies, and expand
OL,18,Fopportunities for cooperation and
OL,19,Finvestment" between the two countries.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]xD@AOU{D@KO]
