FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784852297
OL,3,CTrump says Saudi Arabia must recognise
OL,4,CIsrael under new nuclear pact
OL,6,FUranium enrichment does not
OL,7,Fautomatically lead to the creation of
OL,8,Fa nuclear weapon, as a country would
OL,9,Falso need to develop other
OL,10,Fcapabilities, including the use of
OL,11,Fprecisely timed high explosives.
OL,13,FHowever, the ability to enrich uranium
OL,14,Fcan increase the risk of
OL,15,Fweaponisation, which has been a major
OL,16,Fconcern surrounding Iran's nuclear
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
